Description:
Big House for Big Family in School Zone!!!
Situated right in best area of Clayton South, very well kept, just when you step into the house you will like it, opposite is the Westall Primary School and Secondary College, Westall Shopping Centre and train station.
This brick house on a rectangular block offers four big bedrooms all with built-in-robes, two baths and two toilets and a master bedroom with full ensuite.
All the hard jobs have been done by the owner, just move in and enjoy.
Tidy laundry and spacious kitchen with gas appliances;
Separate lounge offers private entertainment;
Garage and carport with remote control;
All the windows are secured with remote control roller shutters;
A large water tank to save water for planting at the back.
For further information, please contact Kevin Quach 0404 478 666.
